title: Introducing GoDocs Hugo
content: Most of the documentation site are looks identical. Thats why we take an initiative to make something different and bring some new concept with minimal design. Meet Godocs , a documentation and knowledge based website template. It can be used for software, API, frameworks, plugins and templates online documentation website building.
